sourcesContent: const r=({input:r})=>{if(!r||!r.primary[0])return;let o=[r.primary[0]],e=[];for(let e of(r.primary.length>4&&console.warn("You should not specify greater than 4 login methods in `loginMethodsAndOrder.primary`"),r.primary.slice(1)))o.includes(e)?console.warn(`Duplicated login method: ${e}`):o.push(e);for(let n of r.overflow??[])o.includes(n)||e.includes(n)?console.warn(`Duplicated login method: ${n}`):e.push(n);return{primary:o,overflow:e}};export{r as toCustomLoginMethodConfig};
